high_descs: Turn right and go towards the blue bed, turn left before the bed and go straight to the white table.
Pick up the blue pen on the white table.
Turn around and go to the wooden desk behind you.
Put the pen next to the smartphone on the wooden desk.
anns.task_desc: Pick up the blue pen and put it on the wooden desk.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the bed, then turn left and take two steps, then turn right and take one step, then turn left and walk to the desk.
Pick up the blue pen that is on the desk.
Turn to the left and take one step, then turn to the left and walk across the room.
Turn on the lamp that is on the second shelf of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Look at the pen in the lamp light.

high_descs: Go to the right side of the table in front of you, under the window.
Pick up the pen on the right side of the white table.
Turn around and go to the desk to the right of the bed.
Turn on the lamp on the shelf above the desk.
